memberdef.name: Round
memberdef.initializer: do { \ uint32_t t1 = (h) + Sigma1(e) + Ch((e), (f), (g)) + (k) + (w); \ uint32_t t2 = Sigma0(a) + Maj((a), (b), (c)); \ (d) += t1; \ (h) = t1 + t2; \ } while(0)
